      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="create_rules" data-step-uuid="4e5830d2-0933-4c36-ae84-ff47564e1b4d">
    <h2 id="create_rules" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Create Rules</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/751/946/original/64adf450-1e6c-4f0b-b0bc-83c2b7f586e8.png" srcset="" alt="Create Rules" height="513" width="610">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_EFCA3880-1ECF-0135-93EF-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p><span style="color:rgb(38,38,38);">For each Assignment Group, you can create one of three grading rules:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Drop (ignore) the lowest x scores for each student [1].</li>
<li>Drop (ignore) the highest x scores for each student [2].</li>
<li>Never drop a specific assignment [3].</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="drop_lowest_score" data-step-uuid="aa9788e3-5115-4ed0-ab3d-f658e9c5469a">
    <h2 id="drop_lowest_score" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Drop Lowest Score</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/751/952/original/151ff85e-0536-437c-a2d2-f457720873b7.png" srcset="" alt="Drop Lowest Score" height="513" width="610">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_EFCA6940-1ECF-0135-93F1-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To drop a certain number of lowest scores, enter the number in the <strong>Lowest Scores </strong>field. You can use the arrows to adjust the number. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="drop_highest_score" data-step-uuid="33149b83-5e28-41da-a05c-2cdd47e90a68">
