        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/751/944/original/9a587202-d7c3-42c1-b132-4ea20695bac9.png" srcset="" alt="Drop Highest Score" height="513" width="610">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_EFCA9D80-1ECF-0135-93F3-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To drop a certain number of highest scores, enter the number in the <strong>Highest Scores </strong>field. You can use the arrows to adjust the number. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="never_drop_assignment" data-step-uuid="000e71a2-71dc-466b-8203-5c3037b21eaf">
