  <div id="text-content_EFCACE80-1ECF-0135-93F5-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To tell Canvas to never drop a certain assignment, click the <strong>Add an assignment </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="select_assignment" data-step-uuid="329b0514-f628-4fb8-8e86-ef2a03112199">
    <h3 id="select_assignment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Assignment</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/173/776/original/be990098-9282-4b03-90d2-17c08c2c4c0b.png" srcset="" alt="Select Assignment" height="570" width="563">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_EFCAFE60-1ECF-0135-93F7-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Assignment drop-down menu [1], select the name of the assignment in the Assignment Group that should never be dropped.</p>
<p>To select another assignment, click the <strong>Add another assignment </strong>link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
